                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Focus level II affects all spells level 44 and below - which means that they may well be useful a lot higher.  Take Affliction Haste II, for example.  That benefits your levl 29 darkness, which you will use, almost certainly, in preference to higher level darkness spells.  AH1 also works on shorter casting spells than AH2 does - which means it works on FD, whereas AH2 items don't.  So a Bracelet of Woven Grass is actually an awesome item to have.<br /><br />Focus effects do not stack, only one item will have an effect - which you can tell by the activation message when the item does its job.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
                    </tr>
